CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 State Superintendent of Schools – Prolonged State of Emergency – Authority to
3 Declare
4 FOR the purpose of authorizing the State Superintendent of Schools to declare a prolonged
5 state of emergency for an event that prevents regular, in–person attendance at a
6 public school for a specified period of time, subject to certain requirements; and
7 generally relating to the State Superintendent of Schools and a prolonged state of
8 emergency for public schools.
